      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"3. MIHATA TATENASHI built on a nice third two starts back at this track with success over 1200m at this track three-and-a-half weeks ago, getting home by half a length. Hiroshi Chida scored on him last time and retains the mount. Has his share of talent. Hard to beat in this suitable race. 11. JOLLY HARMONY was prominent at the corner and ran a better race last start to finish a close second over 1200m at this track after missing the placings at the previous appearance. Looks well placed so expect another big run. 6. BAKSHEESH ran below expectations when fresh from a spell at this track over 1200m last time. Better placed this time. 8. S K EAGLE has a moderate winning strike-rate but performed well last time at this track, finishing fourth and only 2 lengths from the winner at the end of 1200m. Well placed and should be about the mark.\",\"runners\":[3,11,6,8],\"exclusive\":false}",
